HEADWORD: Digitated
<hw>Dig"i*ta`ted</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>digitatus</ets> having
fingers.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having several leaflets arranged,
like the fingers of the hand, at the extremity of a stem or petiole.
